WEBVTT

57:03.756 --> 57:04.423
Sorry.

57:05.089 --> 57:08.256
Currently, I don't have any
intentions of owning a dog.

57:08.798 --> 57:15.381
Even a lion will become a dog once in its lifetime.

57:16.173 --> 57:17.048
For what?

57:17.964 --> 57:19.298
For the lioness.

57:21.298 --> 57:22.673
I'm crazy about you.

57:23.006 --> 57:25.714
You'll go crazy if you find out
how much I love you.

57:26.381 --> 57:27.756
Marry me.

57:28.464 --> 57:32.673
The whole family can chill without any tension.
